<% include _includes/header %>
<div class="container">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center footer-height">
    <div class="col-md-3 btn-faq">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#whatis" class="m-3">What is Scythe?</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 btn-faq">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#howto" class="m-3">How Do I pay?</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 btn-faq">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#shared" class="m-3">What is a shared account?</button>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- What is Scythe -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="whatis" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="whatIsScythe" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="whatIsScythe">What is Scythe?</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          Sycthe is a website designed around giving it's customers a good price for online accounts whether it be for music, vpns, or even food we have you covered. Our low price and extensive catalog are great so why not go give it a look!
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How to pay -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="howto" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="howToPay" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="howToPay">How Do I Pay?</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          Paying on Scythe is super simple because we accept a large array of different payment methods. You can pay in the normal Paypal or get creative with some cryptocurrency we even accept Amazon Giftcards!
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What is a shared account -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="shared" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="whatIsASharedAccount" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="shared">What is a shared account?</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          I bet you are wondering what exactly 'Shared' means on the different accounts well if you are you have come to the right place. The 'Shared' means that you are sharing the account with someone else and that you aren't the only one on the account. This could cause minor problems but nothing too major!
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<% include _includes/footer %>
